headline: December jobs report, earnings, CES 2026: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime host Jared Blikre previews several of the biggest stories to come next week, including the release of the December jobs report next Friday; earnings results from companies like Constellation Brands (STZ), Albertsons (ACI), Applied Digital (APLD), and Tilray Brands (TLRY); and the start of the 2026 Consumer Electronics Show (CES) on Monday with keynotes from Nvidia (NVDA) CEO Jensen Huang and Advanced Micro Devices (AMD) CEO Lisa Su. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime.
